description:
Everyone's favorite Sonic Underground Characters are back in another exciting episode of Sonic Underground! Bartleby and his boyfriend Sonic find that an arcade at their local mall is giving out a Playstation 5 for only 600,000 tickets! And they will stop at nothing to get their hands on it, even if it means they have to do battle with the evil Dr. Robotnik and his goons Sleet and Dingo!
